" Line Return {{{

" Makes Vim return to the same line when you reopen a file.
if has("autocmd")
    au BufReadPost *
        \ if line("'\"") > 0 && line("'\"") <= line("$") |
            \ exe "normal! g'\"" |
        \ endif
endif

